rio-3840268">在里约热内卢的科帕卡巴纳海滩（Copacabana Beach）进行超过一百万粉丝的巨大免费演出</a>。</p><p> Gaga备受期待的第七张专辑“ Mayhem”定于3月7日发行，可<a href="https://www.ladygaga.com/us-en/shop/collections/mayhem" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订。从2020年代的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/lady-gaga-chromatica-album-review-2677590">“色彩”</a>和她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-announces-joker-2-companion-album-harlequin-3796692">“ Harlequin”同伴记录</a>（2024）之后。</p><p>至于“混乱”的构建，Gaga到目前为止发布了三张单曲：与Bruno Mars， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-lady-gaga-dramatic-new-single-disease-3806194">“疾病”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-gothic-music-video-for-lady-gagas-surprise-new-single-abracadabra-3833942">“ Abracadabra”的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-reveals-die-with-a-smile-with-bruno-mars-huge-part-new-album-3824137">“笑容”</a> 。昨天，她透露了这张专辑的完整歌曲集，其中包括DJ和制片人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gesaffelstein">Gesaffelstein</a>的功能 -<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-lady-gagas-mayhem-tracklist-3839142">在此处查看专辑的完整曲目列表</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3832329" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3832329" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3832329" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Lady Gaga&#39;Mayhem&#39;专辑艺术品。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jp